gobblin.source.extractor.partition

Class Partition

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.source.extractor.partition.Partition

  • public class Partition
extends Object
    This class encapsulates the two ends, lowWatermark and highWatermark, of a partition and some metadata, e.g. hasUserSpecifiedHighWatermark, to describe the partition.

    A Source partitions its data into a collection of Partition, each of which will be used to create a WorkUnit. Currently, the lowWatermark of a partition in Gobblin is inclusive and its highWatermark is exclusive unless it is the last partition.
